sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>(Gateway API /<br/>kube-rbac-proxy)
    participant HTTP as vllm-rocm HTTP<br/>8000/TCP
    participant GRPC as vllm-rocm gRPC<br/>8033/TCP
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine
    participant GPU as AMD ROCm GPU<br/>HIP/ROCm
    participant S3 as Model Storage<br/>(S3 / PVC)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Loading at Startup

    Engine->>S3: Download/mount model weights<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+ (S3)<br/>or filesystem mount (PVC)
    S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts / weights
    Engine->>GPU: Transfer model weights to GPU memory<br/>HIP/ROCm
    GPU-->>Engine: GPU memory allocated

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Model Inference (HTTP - OpenAI API)

    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / Platform AuthN
    Ingress->>HTTP: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000<br/>Auth enforced upstream
    HTTP->>Engine: Process inference request
    Engine->>GPU: Execute LLM forward pass<br/>HIP/ROCm (PagedAttention)
    GPU-->>Engine: Generated tokens
    Engine-->>HTTP: Completion response
    HTTP-->>Ingress: JSON response
    Ingress-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(TLS encrypted)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Inference (gRPC - TGIS)

    Client->>Ingress: gRPC GenerateStream<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS
    Ingress->>GRPC: Forward gRPC request<br/>gRPC/8033
    GRPC->>Engine: Process inference request
    Engine->>GPU: Execute LLM forward pass<br/>HIP/ROCm
    GPU-->>Engine: Generated tokens (streaming)
    Engine-->>GRPC: Token stream
    GRPC-->>Ingress: gRPC stream response
    Ingress-->>Client: Streamed response
